            <h4 className="font-bold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span className="text-lg">💡</span> Pro Tip
            </h4>
            <p className="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed italic">
              "Meta looks for 'Signal' in how you handle constraints. Always mention thermals when discussing AI on glasses."
